</li></ul></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WebAnimation/LaGolda" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WebAnimation/LaGolda">La Golda</a></em>: The kids have one with Juanito the morning after he challenges Ms. Ricca to a soccer match.
</li><li> In <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WebAnimation/RWBYChibi" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WebAnimation/RWBYChibi">RWBY Chibi</a></em>, there was a workout montage where Yang is trying to get fit, complete with a remix of "I Burn" to the tune of <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/Survivor" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/Survivor">"Eye of the Tiger'</a>.
