</li><li> Invoked in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AnsemRetort" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AnsemRetort">Ansem Retort</a></em>, when Axel is about to begin training for a Murder-off.
