</li><li> <a class="urllink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pOcsBiCaEJ8">A montage of training montages<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>.
